course_description: This course builds upon the foundational diagnostic and management skills of WHGRNP Clinical I.  The focus of this course is on delivery of inclusive best practice care to the gynecological patient.
prerequisites: NRSG 763D and NRSG 764D as prerequisites, NRSG 765D as co-requisite, or equivalent transfer credit.
